org.anchoranalysis.core.color

Class ColorList

  • Object
    • ColorList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<RGBColor>, ColorIndex

    public class ColorList
extends Object
implements ColorIndex, Iterable<RGBColor>
    A list of colors, each corresponding to a particular index position.

    Note that a color may be duplicated in more than one position in the list. There is no check on uniqueness.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
